<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="576">Note:</emphasis>
The varietal epithet was spelled 
<normalizedToken originalValue="“dist.nudum”">&quot;dist.nudum&quot;</normalizedToken>
[
<normalizedToken originalValue="“dist.”">&quot;dist.&quot;</normalizedToken>
= 
<normalizedToken originalValue="“distichon”">&quot;distichon&quot;</normalizedToken>
] in the protologue. This was later corrected (Linnaeus, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="576">Sp. Pl.</emphasis>
, ed. 2, 1: 125. 1762) to 
<normalizedToken originalValue="“nudum”">&quot;nudum&quot;</normalizedToken>
. As is established custom, the 
<normalizedToken originalValue="“distichon”">&quot;distichon&quot;</normalizedToken>
is to be ignored under Art. 23.8 and Ex. 19.
</paragraph>
